WEBVTT

00:00:03.919 --> 00:00:11.119
Some of the greatest joys we experience in life are as a result of a happy family life

00:00:11.839 --> 00:00:14.439
But living in these hectic last days

00:00:15.119 --> 00:00:17.359
Achieving such happiness is very difficult

00:00:17.920 --> 00:00:26.679
The governing body deeply appreciates you hard-working parents and all that you're doing to try to help your children find a rich satisfying life

00:00:27.559 --> 00:00:30.399
As a parent I remember the challenge we faced

00:00:31.199 --> 00:00:34.960
Trying to develop love for Jehovah in the hearts of our two little boys

00:00:35.359 --> 00:00:43.960
We use the tools available the Bible watched our articles and then in 1978 how thrilled we were to receive

00:00:44.479 --> 00:00:48.840
My book of Bible stories what a godsend this proof to be

00:00:50.280 --> 00:00:58.320
Over the years the governing body has provided many additional teaching aids to help our young ones and we have no intention of stopping there

00:00:58.880 --> 00:01:00.880
It is a fact that

00:01:00.880 --> 00:01:06.719
Animated videos capture the interest of little ones and can be a powerful teaching tool

00:01:07.920 --> 00:01:15.519
Hence it's my privilege on behalf of the governing body to introduce to you a new animated video series entitled

00:01:16.120 --> 00:01:18.120
Be Comja Hova's Friend

00:01:18.359 --> 00:01:22.719
This is just a preview of what we have in store for you in the future

00:01:24.480 --> 00:01:27.599
Children can learn so much during their formative years

00:01:28.079 --> 00:01:33.359
Lessons they learn at a very young age can make an impression that lasts a lifetime

00:01:34.239 --> 00:01:40.799
It is our prayer that this new series will help your children to learn to make God's heart rejoice

00:01:42.079 --> 00:01:44.079
We love you very much

00:01:44.159 --> 00:01:50.319
But our love for you is just a reflection of Jehovah's great love for you and your little ones

00:01:51.200 --> 00:01:52.879
May they learn

00:01:52.879 --> 00:01:56.959
Develop and grow to become Jehovah's Friend
